home.description: This is the production version of Nexpy's boilerplate frontend. This boilerplate is based on Typescript and Next.js and it's open source.
home.use: You can use it in your projects and templates, or contribute with improvements and new features!
internal.dialog.server_error: An internal server error has occurred and the error data has already been automatically sent to support. Try again later.
internal.dialog.offline: Apparently you are offline. Check your internet connection and try again.
internal.dialog.not_found: The resource you are trying to access either does not exist or has been permanently moved. But you can still browse amazing things by browsing the rest of the site.
